<br>
This would be a good spell progression:<br>
at  1st: DD, Caster cenered AoE, shield, and Bolt.<br>
at  4th: DD, Mob centered AoE, Direct Damage Buff<br>
at  8th: DD, Rain AoE, Bolt, skin, 0-stun<br>
at 12th: DD, Caster cenered AoE, shield, bolt<br>
at 16th: DD, Mob centered AoE, Direct Damage Buff<br>
at 20th: DD, Rain AoE, DDB, Bolt, skin, 6-stun<br>
<br>
Progress like that. the DDBs should be targetable, and the damage unresistable. They turn into group spells around 24th and 29th they turn into group buffs, and the stun line turns into AoEs. <p>Ennya Orcsbane<BR>
1st Elder of The Tears Of Veeshan<BR>
